To cite internal-fluid-flow in publications use:

  Umpierre, Alexandre Perez. (2022). iboot: A toolbox for internal fluid flow based on the Poiseuille condition and the Colebrooke-White and the Darcy-Weissbach equations.
  https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3992392

A BibTeX entry for LaTeX users is:

  @manual{,
    title     = {{iboot}: A toolbox for internal fluid flow based on the Poiseuille condition and the Colebrooke-White and the Darcy-Weissbach equations.},
    author    = {Alexandre Perez Umpierre},
    year      = {2022},
  }